OpenSearchServer,is,an,open,source,search,engine,based,on,continuously,improving,open,source,technology,Through,their,SaaS,center,users,can,access,a,public,API,The,Screenshot,API,allows,users,to,make,a,screenshot,capture,of,a,Web,page,The,user,can,choose,to,capture,only,the,visible,part,of,the,page,or,the,full,content,The,service,uses,REST,calls,and,returns,a,PNG,image,which,can,still,be,reduced,to,generate,a,thumbnail,An,account,is,required,with,service,and,API,Key,is,used,to,access,the,API